title: Expert or Jenny Friend: Is He a Professional Pianist or Not?
description: Jenny has someone on the show named Otto that she claims is a professional piano player.   Dave and Falen ask him questions to try to figure out if he is really a professional piano player or just one of Jenny's friends pretending to be a professional piano player.
